<body>
<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1039146" n="1"/> 
  <opener><salute>Viro Doctissimo <rs type="person"><abbr>Fr.</abbr> <abbr>Lud.</abbr> Spr<choice><orig><g ref="#ydots">ÿ</g></orig><reg>y</reg></choice>nglino</rs> Amico suo singulari et <abbr>pl.</abbr> colendo
      <lb/><abbr>S. P. D.</abbr> <rs type="person"><abbr>Nic.</abbr> Bernoull<choice><orig><g ref="#j">j</g></orig><reg>i</reg></choice></rs>.</salute></opener>
<p><lb/><rs type="lostletter">Literas</rs> Tuas humanissimas, quibus ad <rs type="letter">meas</rs> tam cito, quod su<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>i erga me amoris indicium est, mihi
  <lb/>respondere dignatus es, su<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>a cum voluptate perlegi, et ex iis me non ultimum inter amicos Tuos
  <lb/>locum adhucdum obtinere l<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>tus percepi, de quo proin mihi impense gratulor. Illud autem
  <lb/>quod significas, Te nempe promissa impleturum et sub finem <date>hujus mensis</date> <rs type="place">Basile<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> futurum
  <lb/>esse, conceptam illam antehac ex disjunctione nostra tristitiam, quam fere omnem jam ex ani<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>mo excusseram, renovavit imo et auxit; illud etenim, quo me erigebam, solatium et spes qu<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice>
  <lb/>constanter fovebam, me Te <rs type="place">Basile<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> hac <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>state visurum, Tuoque ibidem fruiturum colloquio,
  <lb/>ipso illo tempore, quo suavissimas Tuas <rs type="letter">literas</rs> accepi, subito proh dolor! evanuit. Accidens
  <lb/>aliquod haud pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>visum me discessum meum in mensem <date>Septembrem</date> rejicere, atque adeo exopta<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tissima Tua pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>sentia <date>hoc a<choice><orig><g ref="#nn">n̄</g></orig><reg>nn</reg></choice>o</date> carere cogit; dico hoc <date>anno</date>: nos enim post reditum Tuum in
  <lb/><rs type="place">Patriam</rs>, si non <rs type="place">Basile<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs>, saltem in alio quodam <rs type="place">Helveti<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> loco, aliquando conjunctum iri
  <lb/>confido. Interim donec hoc contingat amicitia nostra majora indies capiet incrementa, si
  <lb/>moto potis est capere, quid enim ad su<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>um amorem amplius accedere queat, nondum scio;
  <lb/>ego saltem me totum Tibi et ad qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>vis officia paratum sisto. Quid vero Tibi in itinere pro<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>posito <rs type="place">Basile<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>sentia mea et officiis, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> forte Tibi ibidem pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>stare possem, carendum erit,
  <lb/>alium Tibi in mei locum substituo, amicum nempe meum singularem <rs type="person">Franciscum Christ</rs> Juris
  <lb/>Studiosum, quem rogo ut meo nomine salutes; is non cessabit in mei gratiam co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>odis Tuis,
  <lb/>si quomodo potuerit, inservire, Teque etiam amico nostro co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>uni <rs type="person">Emanueli Thurnisio</rs> Bi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>bliopol<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>, quem ut spero itineris <rs type="place">Francofurtani</rs> socium habebis, facile co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>endabit. Salu<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tabis etiam, si placet, <abbr>Cl.</abbr> <abbr>Prof.</abbr> <rs type="person">Iselium</rs> et <rs type="person">Patruum</rs> meum, quorum prior Te fortasse <rs type="letter">lite<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ris</rs> <rs type="place">Marburgum</rs> perferendis onerabit. <rs type="biblio">Librum</rs> illum et ocreas, si eas <del><gap/></del>Tecum assume<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>re Tibi co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>odum sit, in nostras vel etiam <rs type="person">Patrui</rs> mei <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>des, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> nostris contigu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> sunt,
  <lb/>mitti curabis. Rogo Te quoque, ut <rs type="place">Marburgi</rs> <abbr>D.</abbr> <abbr>Prof.</abbr> <rs type="person">Harscherum</rs>, si eum compellatione
  <lb/>Tua dignaberis, meo nomine salutes. Ecce amice optime, libere Tecum ago in mandatis
  <lb/>Tibi dandis, rogo proinde, ut pari libertate utaris, quotiescunque me Tibi quadam
  <lb/>in re inservire posse deprehendes. C<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>terum iter Tuum felix et prosperum esse jubeat. 
  <pb facs="1039147" n="2"/> 
  <lb/><abbr>D. O. M.</abbr> qui Te illo ex animi sententia absoluto sospitem et incolumem domum reducat, ubi
  <lb/>ut brevi tempore eruditionis et studiorum Tuorum digna pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>mia consequaris, est quod Tibi
  <lb/>animitus apprecor. </p><closer>Vale et me ama. <dateline>Dabam <rs type="place">Parisiis</rs> <date when="1710-08-11">11. Augusti 1710</date>. <rs type="place"><hi rend="u">Genevam</hi></rs></dateline></closer>
<postscript>
<p><abbr>P. S.</abbr> <rs type="person">Risoldo</rs> navem suam remitto, et c<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>teros <rs type="person">amicos</rs> omnes plurimum salvere jubeo.</p>
</postscript>
</div>
